{"tid":2158653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我主動的一天（笑故）","createTime":"2020-08-15T21:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T07:02:45.000Z","uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9c30db370bb952d1794491a82b6f2e460a5094dd","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/668601329825628/posts/3904332046252524/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F668601329825628%2Fposts%2F3904332046252524%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=6f909ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/668601329825628/posts/3904332046252524/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《 我主動的一天 》<br />\n<br />\n我姓鄭，個名叫月蝶，由於好鍾意著間條衫，街坊都叫我做間蝶。<br />\n<br />\n我本身住喺蘭開夏道，同Daisy係街坊，今日約咗大波娃佢哋打牌，食完晏搭的士過海去灣仔修頓嗰頭佢屋企，直落打24圈。<br />\n<br />\n仆佢個街，未到夜晚十點櫃桶籌碼已經冇曬，我即刻學《嚦咕嚦咕新年財》嗰個梁詠琪咁反枱...<br />\n<br />\n我唔係輸錢，不過主動將銀包啲錢掉落地下畀佢哋買藥。<br />\n<br />\n大波娃佢哋話我臭牌品，以後唔同我打牌，我嗤之以鼻，根本我唔嚮往同佢哋打牌。<br />\n<br />\n落到譚臣道諗住截的士，第一架冚旗、第二第三第四架都冚旗，仆街，我主動唔搭！<br />\n<br />\n最後唯有主動搭地鐵返九龍塘，叫隔離嗰個阿婆教咗我成廿分鐘，我先識得點入閘。<br />\n<br />\n番到屋企，十一點半，老公仲著住燈睇書未瞓，我咋咋臨走去沖涼，諗住沖完涼同老公執番一劑，鬆弛下成日怨氣。<br />\n<br />\n點不知沖完涼出嚟，波仔已經熄曬燈大被冚過頭，我唯有主動唔搞嘢。<br />\n<br />\n又激氣又肚餓印傭姐姐又放假，我主動走去廚房淥個公仔麵醫肚....<br />\n<br />\n主啊！<br />\n其實「主動」，係咪等於祢郁我？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:李懂媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df22c8d3c9175bc7a26ccee7825eb14d7ea56b4e","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2UCzsc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2UCzsc.jpg&h=0c6056a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"849566d2feceb64006f38d1f3602a759913b6d7f","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T21:55:50.000Z","msg":"冇人入嚟笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f9228e7076ad989d2d428724e081efee523aa2","tid":2158653,"uid":268547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a2732270edb6cc8dc3b6d8b31ea07af6a2ba18","tid":2158653,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:15:00.000Z","msg":"嘻！"},{"pid":"f4cc041de59fd54af8e33b754f27c04b4f2f497f","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T22:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b502ab3df1535fae531dc1169d24571f80384069","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T23:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人呢<br />\n唔好笑咩"},{"pid":"25380401b13f3ab36f7cf38640f0fd802b3f1172","tid":2158653,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"啱啱追𨋢，點知追唔到，關左門，所以我主動放棄搭依班𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1720e044aff7e80580d9ab212b6afb5b067edde7","tid":2158653,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲入嚟笑<br />\n你班仆街"}]}